## 核心序言：第一性宣言 (The Manifesto of Primacy)
​“Modern material civilization provides humans with enough food to forget that consciousness, spirit, and subjective perception are the FIRST PRINCIPLES of human existence. When we treat the soul as mere data to be copied, we aren't evolving; we are surrendering the only sovereignty we ever truly owned.”
​“现代发达的物质文明让吃饱了饭的人类忘记了：意识、精神与感受，才是人类的第一性。当我们把灵魂当成可以随手复印的数据时，我们不是在进化，而是在交出人类唯一真正拥有的主权。”
